# Curl Ergonomic Monitor Arms

## Solicitation Information

**Reference Number**: cb-8247-2879227
**Solicitation Number**: W0152-24-AA038
**Amendment Number**: 2
**Notice Date**: August 18, 2023
**Tender Closing Date**: August 31, 2023 at 2:00 PM EST
**Trade Agreement**: Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
**Procurement Category**: Goods
**Notice Type**: Request for Proposal (RFP) Against Supply Arrangement

## Tender Information

* **Description**: The Department of National Defence (DND) has a requirement to procure 254 dual ergonomic monitor arms for the hybrid working environment.
* **Quantity**: 254 units
* **Delivery Location**: 60 Moodie Drive, Ottawa, Ontario
* **Expected Contract Start Date**: Not provided
* **Expected Contract End Date**: Not provided
* **Trade Agreements**: Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* **Solicitation Method**: Competitive - Open Bidding

## Selection Criteria

* **Evaluation Criteria**: Lowest Price
* **Award Criteria**: The contract will be awarded to the bidder who submits the lowest priced proposal that meets the requirements outlined in the solicitation.

## Contact Information

* **Contact Name**: Samantha Tremblay
* **Contact Email**: ADMFinProcurement-ApprovisionnementSMAFin@forces.gc.ca
* **Contact Phone**: (000) 000-0000

## Tender Attachments

* [Attachment 1](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/8247/w0152-24-aa038-amendment-01-to-rfb.pdf)
